  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK686">
<l>kaṟṟukkaṇ ṇañcāṉ celaccollik kālattāṟ </l>
<l>ṟakka taṟivatān tūtu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is an ambassador who having studied (politics) talks impressively, is not afraid of angry looks, and knows (to employ) the art suited to the time.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
